# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Pretty URLs: /about works without the .html extension.
# Cloudflare Pages auto-resolves /about -> /about.html, so this file mostly
# handles legacy redirects from the old GoDaddy Website Builder site.

# Old GoDaddy paths → new pages
/minis        /programs       301
/juniors      /programs       301
/questions    /contact        301
/questions%3F /contact        301
/register     /tryouts        301

# www -> apex (optional; flip if you prefer www)
# https://www.swrfc.com/*  https://swrfc.com/:splat  301

# Note: 404 handling for Workers Static Assets is configured in
# wrangler.jsonc via `assets.not_found_handling`, not here. The old
# `/* /404.html 404` line that worked on legacy Pages is not valid
# here — only 200/301/302/303/307/308 are accepted.
